        <p class="mt-6 text-muted">
          多数 2019 年后的国行 / 海外设备选 <strong class="text-ink">arm64-v8a</strong>。老设备或不确定就用 universal。
          Google Play 上架走 AAB（开发者侧）。所有包均由 GitHub Actions release.yml 签名出包。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {apkArm64 && (
          <a
            href={apkArm64.href}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border-2 border-ember bg-ember/5 hover:bg-ember/10 transition-all block"
          >
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-3">
              <div class="font-mono text-xs text-ember">ARM64-V8A · 推荐</div>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-ember">{apkArm64.label}</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-3xl mb-2">app-arm64-v8a-release.apk</h3>
            <div class="text-sm text-ink mb-3">64-bit ARM 设备 · Android 8.0+ · 主流首选</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-muted">小米 / 红米 / 华为 / OPPO / vivo / 一加 / 三星 / Pixel 等 2019+</div>
            <div class="mt-6 text-sm text-ember">下载 APK ↓</div>
          </a>
        )}

        {apkUniversal && (
          <a
            href={apkUniversal.href}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-line hover:border-ember hover:bg-ember/5 transition-all block"
          >
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-3">
              <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted">UNIVERSAL</div>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-muted">{apkUniversal.label}</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-3xl mb-2">app-universal-release.apk</h3>
            <div class="text-sm text-ink mb-3">通用包 · 双架构合一 · 不确定就用这个</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-muted">体积更大但兼容所有 ARM 架构 · 一包通吃</div>
            <div class="mt-6 text-sm text-ember opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">下载 APK ↓</div>
          </a>
        )}

        {apkArmV7 && (
          <a
            href={apkArmV7.href}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-line hover:border-ember hover:bg-ember/5 transition-all block"
          >
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-3">
              <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted">ARMEABI-V7A</div>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-muted">{apkArmV7.label}</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-3xl mb-2">app-armeabi-v7a-release.apk</h3>
            <div class="text-sm text-ink mb-3">32-bit ARM · 老设备 fallback</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-muted">2018 年前的低端设备 · 体积最小</div>
            <div class="mt-6 text-sm text-ember opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">下载 APK ↓</div>
          </a>
        )}

        {aab && (
          <a
            href={aab.href}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-line hover:border-ember hover:bg-ember/5 transition-all block"
          >
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-3">
              <div class="font-mono text-xs text-muted">AAB · DEVELOPER</div>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-muted">{aab.label}</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-3xl mb-2">app-release.aab</h3>
            <div class="text-sm text-ink mb-3">Android App Bundle · Google Play 上架专用</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-muted">不是给终端用户的直装包 —— 普通用户请选 APK</div>
            <div class="mt-6 text-sm text-ember opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">下载 AAB ↓</div>
          </a>
        )}
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-cream/70 border border-line text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
        <strong class="text-ink">安装说明：</strong> 国行设备首次安装本地 APK 需在系统设置允许"来自此来源的应用"。
        Android 自更新由应用内 <code class="font-mono bg-paper px-1 rounded">设置 → 检查更新</code> 入口走 GitHub
        Releases <code class="font-mono bg-paper px-1 rounded">{ANDROID_TAG}</code> tag → DownloadManager →
        REQUEST_INSTALL_PACKAGES 闭环。iOS 版本即将上线。
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-muted text-center">
        看一下完整版本说明？前往 <a href={ANDROID_RELEASE_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-ember hover:underline">GitHub Release {ANDROID_TAG} ↗</a>
        或 <a href="https://github.com/chainlesschain/chainlesschain/blob/main/android-app/CHANGELOG.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-ember hover:underline">Android CHANGELOG ↗</a>
      </p>
    </div>
